cess the login page.'=>'NinjaFirewall will always enforce the HTTP authentication or captcha implementation each time you access the login page.','You can choose two different types of protection: a password or a captcha. You can enable the protection only if an attack is detected or to keep it always activated.'=>'You can choose two different types of protection: a password or a captcha. You can enable the protection only if an attack is detected or to keep it always activated.','Message (max. 1024 characters, HTML tags allowed)'=>'Message (max. 1024 characters, HTML tags allowed)','Please enter max 1024 character only.'=>'Please enter max 1024 character only.','NinjaFirewall is not compatible with Microsoft Windows.'=>'NinjaFirewall is not compatible with Microsoft Windows.','PHP has several wrappers for use with the filesystem functions. It is possible for an attacker to use them to bypass firewalls and various IDS to exploit remote and local file inclusions. This option lets you block any script attempting to pass a <code>expect://</code>, <code>file://</code>, <code>phar://</code>, <code>php://</code>, <code>zip://</code> or <code>data://</code> stream inside a <code>GET</code> or <code>POST</code> request, cookies, user agent and referrer variables.'=>'PHP has several wrappers for use with the filesystem functions. It is possible for an attacker to use them to bypass firewalls and various IDS to exploit remote and local file inclusions. This option lets you block any script attempting to pass a <code>expect://</code>, <code>file://</code>, <code>phar://</code>, <code>php://</code>, <code>zip://</code> or <code>data://</code> stream inside a <code>GET</code> or <code>POST</code> request, cookies, user agent and referrer variables.','Error: Wrong rules format.'=>'Error: Wrong rules format.','Full or partial case-sensitive string(s), max. 255 characters. Multiple values must be comma-separated'=>'Full or partial case-sensitive string(s), max. 255 characters. Mult