tion console</a>.','Cannot retrieve user rules from database (#3)'=>'Cannot retrieve user rules from the database (#3)','Cannot retrieve user rules from database (#2)'=>'Cannot retrieve user rules from the database (#2)','Cannot retrieve user options from database (#3)'=>'Cannot retrieve user options from the database (#3)','Cannot retrieve user options from database (#2)'=>'Cannot retrieve user options from the database (#2)','Cannot connect to WordPress database'=>'Cannot connect to the WordPress database','Cannot retrieve WordPress database credentials'=>'Cannot retrieve WordPress database credentials','Cannot read WordPress configuration file'=>'Cannot read WordPress configuration file','Cannot find WordPress configuration file'=>'Cannot find WordPress configuration file','A true Web Application Firewall to protect and secure WordPress.'=>'A true Web Application Firewall to protect and secure WordPress.','Administrator account'=>'Administrator account ','Total administrators : %s'=>'Total administrators : %s','NinjaFirewall has detected that one or more administrator accounts were modified in the database:'=>'NinjaFirewall has detected that one or more administrator accounts were modified in the database:','[NinjaFirewall] Alert: Database changes detected'=>'[NinjaFirewall] Alert: Database changes detected','Review your installation, your site is not protected.'=>'Review your installation. Your site is not protected.','NinjaFirewall fatal error:'=>'NinjaFirewall fatal error:','unknown error'=>'unknown error','%s directory is read-only. Please review your installation and ensure that %s is writable.'=>'%s directory is read-only. Please review your installation and ensure that %s is writable.','%s directory cannot be created. Please review your installation and ensure that %s is writable.'=>'%s directory cannot be created. Please review your installation and ensure that %s is writable.','NinjaFirewall error'=>'NinjaFirewall error','View firewall log'=>'View firewall log','Medium:'=>'Medium:','High:'=>'High:','Critical:'=>'Critical:','NinjaFirewall Statistics'=>'NinjaFirewall Statistics','Compare</a> the WP and <font color="#21759B">WP+</font> Editions.'=>'Compare</a> the WP and <font color="#21759B">WP+</font> Editions.','Learn more</a> about the <font color="#21759B">WP+</font> Edition unique features.'=>'Learn more</a> about the <font color="#21759B">WP+</font> Edition\'s unique features.','This allows easier and faster inter-process communication between the firewall and the plugin part of NinjaFirewall and, because its data and configuration are stored in shared memory segments, the firewall does not need to connect to the database any longer.'=>'This allows easier and faster inter-process communication between the firewall and the plugin part of NinjaFirewall and, because its data and configuration are stored in shared memory segments, the firewall does not need to connect to the database any longer.','Although NinjaFirewall is already <a href="%s">much faster than other WordPress plugins</a>, the <b><font color="#21759B">WP+</font> Edition</b> brings its performance to a whole new level by using Unix shared memory in order to speed things up even more.'=>'Although NinjaFirewall is already <a href="%s">much faster than other WordPress plugins</a>, the <b><font color="#21759B">WP+</font> Edition</b> brings its performance to a whole new level by using Unix shared memory in order to speed things up even more.','Improved features'=>'Improved features','NinjaFirewall antispam feature works only with WordPress built-in comment and registration forms.'=>'The NinjaFirewall antispam feature works only with WordPress built-in comment and registration forms.','Notification'=>'Notification','Access Control'=>'Access Control','Rules version:'=>'Rules version:','NinjaFirewall security rules have been updated:'=>'NinjaFirewall security rules have been updated:','[NinjaFirewall] Security rules update'=>'[NinjaFirewall] Security rules 